<section class="home-testimonials">

    <div class="testimonials-container">
        <div>
            <h1 class="testimonial-title">Here's what</h1>
            <h1 class="testimonial-title">others are saying.</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card-container"> 
            <div class="testimonial-card long">
                <img class="testimonial-img" src="@asset('images/gwen.png')" alt="">
                <p class="testimonial-text">I had the opportunity to work with Sean in a transaction and it was such a pleasure. It turned out to be the most seamless, painless transaction I have experienced. He did everything he promised to do within the time frame. His attorney was very responsive in getting documents prepared in a timely manner. I highly recommend Sean Brella or Brella Ventures as a buyer/seller and I hope to have the opportunity to work with him again.</p>
                <div class="card-bottom">
                    <div class="bottom-left">
                        <p class="testimonial-name">Gwen F.</p>
                        <div>
